sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Engine as Reminder engine
    participant Parent as Parent device
    participant API as CareBridge API
    actor Caregiver
    participant Local as Local contact

    Engine->>Parent: Local + privacy-safe push reminder
    Parent-->>Engine: No response during grace period
    Engine->>API: Mark reminder Missed
    API-->>Caregiver: Care alert needs attention
    Caregiver->>API: Ring now
    API->>API: Rate-limit + authorize request
    API->>Parent: Remote alarm push
    Parent-->>API: Delivered / opened / actioned / failed
    API-->>Caregiver: Live delivery tracking

    alt Parent responds
        Parent->>API: Taken / Need Help
        API-->>Caregiver: Updated event state
        Caregiver->>API: Resolve
    else Delivery uncertain or failed
        Caregiver->>Parent: Phone call
        Caregiver->>Local: Notify trusted local contact
        Local-->>Caregiver: Situation update
        Caregiver->>API: Resolve with note
    end
